<p><b>Abstract</b> </p>
<p>Screenie <a href="data/screenie.gz">screenie [.sh/.gz, 2.3kb]</a>&nbsp;
is a small and leightweight screen-session handler for administering
SCREEN(1) jobs easier by using an interactive menu.<br>
Send me hints, comments, ideas, bugreports and testreports (tested on
which operating-system and architecture?) to the e-mail address below.<br>
&nbsp; </p>
